deal MHD-model is developed with\naccount of recent results on imagery of the solar wind speed in the corona up\nto 5.5 solar radii obtained on the basis of combined observations from\nSOHO/UVCS, LASCO, and Mauna Loa.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jun 2018 17:59:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 20:58:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-11"}
