 neither the number nor type of mutants utilized dramatically impact\nmeasures of TCP effectiveness under typical experimental settings. Finally, our\nsimilarity analysis illustrates that highly prioritized test cases tend to\nuncover dissimilar faults.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 03:01:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
