 increase the material\nstandard of living much beyond Earth while increasing the total mass per person\nrelatively little.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 06:40:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Sep 2018 05:13:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2019 09:44:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-13"}
