essure, so the\ndust clouds must have formed within months. The modern infrared observations\nwere taken at a time when there was at least 12.4% +- 1.3% dust coverage (as\npart of the secular dimming), and this is consistent with dimming originating\nin circumstellar dust.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 11:16:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-11"}
