o demonstrate the estimation of the\n2PL testlet model with the three estimation methods.\n  Keywords: IRT, testlet model, estimation, full-information,\nlimited-information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 14:07:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
