coherent\noscillations between the constituents of this hybrid quantum system. These\nresults enable a new class of experiments exploring the use of the two-qubit\ninteractions mediated by microwave photons to create entangled states between\nsemiconductor and superconducting qubits. The methods and techniques presented\nhere are transferable to QD devices based on other material systems and can be\nbeneficial for spin-based hybrid systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 14:56:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-16"}
